AB  - In this note we derive a sufficient condition and necessary condition for the adoption of free trade to decrease savings in terms of any good in a model with two traded goods and one non-traded good. We assume more generally than Pattanaik, and following Pasinetti, that a fraction of total capital is owned by labor.
